<br>
I just park my pet by the FM zone for saftey and solo my ass off.. If you stay near the wall there are hardly any adds, and you have Dark Blues into the 40's..<br>
<br>
I used focus Earth pet with DS, BOII, Chain Armour, Swords of Runes.  I pulled with Malaise.. heal nuke rinse and repeat.. C3 helps alot to overcome down time..  Teaming with a Necro who can fear is even better.. (no downtime) I got 1 yellow bub an hour at least..<br>
<br>
Now at 41 am soloing in DL by FM using the same method..<br>
<br>
Give it a try!<br>
