<br>
1. C only costs about 50pp and solo the drops in OT will at leasts recover that investment in the 2.5 hours that you have it.  The Rhino's sometimes drop 4pp even!<br>
It is safe, and yes there may be down time, but you will still level faster than getting in a group there.. unless..<br>
<br>
2. I 've probably said this too many times, but it is so true if done correctly. You group with a toon that has fear.. druid/necro..<br>
